sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Browser
    participant Frontend
    participant Backend
    participant OAuth as Manus OAuth
    participant DB as Database
    
    User->>Browser: Click "Login"
    Browser->>Frontend: Navigate to login
    Frontend->>Frontend: Generate login URL
    Frontend->>OAuth: Redirect to OAuth portal
    
    User->>OAuth: Enter credentials
    OAuth->>OAuth: Validate credentials
    OAuth->>Backend: Callback with auth code
    
    Backend->>OAuth: Exchange code for token
    OAuth-->>Backend: Return access token
    Backend->>OAuth: Fetch user profile
    OAuth-->>Backend: Return user data
    
    Backend->>DB: Check if user exists
    alt User exists
        DB-->>Backend: Return user record
    else New user
        Backend->>DB: Create user record
        DB-->>Backend: Return new user
    end
    
    Backend->>Backend: Create session
    Backend->>Backend: Sign JWT token
    Backend-->>Browser: Set session cookie
    Browser->>Frontend: Redirect to dashboard
    
    Frontend->>Backend: Request user data (with cookie)
    Backend->>Backend: Verify JWT token
    Backend->>DB: Fetch user details
    DB-->>Backend: Return user data
    Backend-->>Frontend: Return authenticated user
    Frontend->>User: Show dashboard
    
    Note over User,Frontend: Subsequent Requests
    Frontend->>Backend: API call (with cookie)
    Backend->>Backend: Verify session
    alt Valid session
        Backend-->>Frontend: Return data
    else Invalid/expired
        Backend-->>Frontend: 401 Unauthorized
        Frontend->>User: Redirect to login
    end
